* phase-5 tail: EIS instructions (type 27) via MFSCAN.  MLR/CMPC are K=1 (two
* MFs + two values); AD2D is K=5, AD3D K=6 (three operand descriptors).  The
* second MLR uses the (ar,rl,id,reg) paren MF form, whose AR bit moves into the
* opcode field.
       MLR   5,6,0,1
       CMPC  3,4,7,0
       AD2D  1,2,3,4,5
       AD3D  1,2,3,4,5,6
       MLR   (1,0,0,2),6,0,0
       END
